 "remarks": "A beautiful Stamford move-in ready townhouse condo in Glenbrook neighborhood. The main level offers open living and entertaining with the kitchen, living room and access to the terrace along with a convenient powder room. Upstairs you&apos;ll find primary bedroom suite, a spacious 2nd bedroom, full bath plus a versatile loft space that can be used as an office, reading nook or guest area. The lower level is equally functional featuring a walk-out layout with a garage, extra parking and a dedicated workout room/gym space and a separate laundry room. 2023 all new windows and new AC unit on 1st floor. 2nd floor AC is about 3 years old. What truly stands out is the walkability - enjoy walking distance to shops, restaurants, groceries and Metro North making commuting and errands effortless.",
